fullplot: Jessica Yu's documentary explores the relationship between human life and Euripidean dramatic structure by weaving together the stories of four men: German terrorist, a bank robber, an "ex-gay" evangelist, and a martial arts student.

title: Protagonist

tomatoes.consensus: Protagonist skillfully intertwines its subjects' lives through an unexpected common thread -- Euripedes.
